data.description: Under contract-accepting backup offers. PRICE IMPROVEMENT!! HURRY in to see this fabulous villa TODAY! Sit outside and enjoy the glorious Florida weather from your lanai overlooking lake views and watch the abundant wildlife that it attracts. Completely updated villa inside plus NEW ROOF. Kitchen offers GRANITE counters, stone backsplash, stainless steel sink, updated faucets, fixtures and STAINLESS STEEL appliances. Plenty of cabinets and large pantry. Open floor plan with pass through to kitchen with plenty of room for guests to cozy up to the bar counter or lay out a spread for all to enjoy. Laminate floors throughout the villa. NO CARPETS. Extended living space offers room for den, office, or dining room. PLANTATION SHUTTERS grace the windows. Spacious master bedroom with en suite bathroom which has been UPDATED with GRANITE counter, new faucets and fixtures, cabinets and sink, updated tile in shower with niche and seamless glass door. Walk in closet. Guest bedroom at other end of the villa for everyone's privacy. Guest bath has also been updated with new sink, cabinet, faucet and fixtures. Laundry room has STACKABLE WASHER AND DRYER and space was created for extra storage. SOME FURNISHINGS AVAILABLE SEPARATELY. Pelican Pointe is Venice's Premier community offering resort style amenities including Clubhouse with bar/grill, card room/library, and banquet facilities. Heated pool with lap lanes for swimming, fitness center, tennis courts and pickle ball, tons of sidewalks for enjoying the weather throughout the community, and 27 holes of golf with Pro Shop. Golf is NOT mandatory. All of this Centrally located minutes to Venice Beach, Venice Downtown, shopping, theatres, restaurants, highways, airports, and so much more. Venice is the quaint gem you have been looking for. SEASON IS COMING .  SEE THIS VILLA BEFORE SOMEONE ELSE GETS IT!! Come find YOUR Florida Lifestyle today. 3D WALK THROUGH tour at :https://my.matterport.com/show/?m=bTfrgmGpujQ
